> schedule:
>
>
>
>
>
> *Fixed Income*
>
> *Equity*
>
> Up to GBP 250k
>
> 0.35%
>
> 0.40%
>
> GBP 250k-500k
>
> 0.30%
>
> 0.35%
>
> Above GBP 500k
>
> 0.20%
>
> 0.25%
>
>
>
> Our standard *custody*/account fee is 25bps , however we are happy to
> reduce this to 15bps for you.
>
>
>
> From speaking to the portfolio managers, we are under the impression that
